title: Arista Switches: Temperature Sensors
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/arista
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the temperature sensors of Arista Networks switches
 via the SNMP ENTITY-SENSOR-MIB (entPhySensorTable) combined with the
 entity descriptions. Sensors reporting their unit as Celsius are
 monitored.

 In addition to the configurable temperature levels (rule "Temperature")
 the sensor's own status is evaluated: status 1 is {OK}, status 2 is
 {WARN}.

discovery:
 One service is created for each Celsius sensor that reports a value.
 Sensors whose name starts with "PhyAlaska" are skipped.

item:
 The entity description of the sensor.
